rules.successText: Engine is turning on, you get engine data

default.name: Communication Engineer N.B. Parker
default.journalTask: Communication Engineer N.B. Parker  need a "Engine Data" (give Red Card) Engine room is in the left side of the factory

dialogAnswers.text: Hi my name is Parker i am a Communication Engineer here on platform, i can help you to turn on the surface scanner
The scanner located on the upper floor right side of the platform, this sector is closed you need a Red Card, i can give it to you if you launch the platform Engine, talk to Captain Turner about that
Great, what kind of things you are looking on the surface?

questions.text: I need to find something deep under ground, 1.5 km deep, it should be a electromagnetic signal i have a setup for the scanner

dialogAnswers.text: Hm.... usually we scan the surface to find some minerals and make map, detect surface features, but you need to find electromagnetic activity, for that purpose you need to use two Relay Station a large Hi-gain antenna near the station. To power up the Relay Station you need to find a Power Cell its a large white console, located on the left side of the factory, good luck

questions.text: Ok i launch the platform engine and find the Power Cell for Relay Station

dialogAnswers.text: Did you powered up the engine? if yes i will give Red Card to you
I hope you find what you are looking for

rules.successText: you get the object 4 processed signal, you can move on

default.name: Bridge Communication Terminal
default.journalTask: Get  "surface signal object 4" from scanner in upper right partof the factory

dialogAnswers.text: This is Communication Terminal of the station "Ashur Station"
Yes yes this is Doctor Edward here you loud and clear, glad to here you from Venus Ashur Station, how are you?

questions.text: Yes i am just arrive to the station

dialogAnswers.text: Now you need to find Surface mineralogy scan computer, and find signal of the Sphere 4
Did you get the data of Sphere №4 signal?, if Yes i need a minutes to download and analyze it

Great news we can trace the signal its very week, and with interference, but i found what i want thank you, you made it, now you need to fly to the Mars, the gate is in operation mode so just fly through it,next contact will be on Mars Alpha Side Colony.

default.name: Captain J.N. Turner
default.journalTask: Captain J.N. Turner need 10 evidence of destroyed enemy (give Green Card)

dialogAnswers.text: Hello Major!! I am Captain Turner, this is the "Altera" company platform, we know about you arrived, the communication with Earth is Restored an we can send the files and data to Earth
This is a Carbon Dioxide processing factory we produce a different materials and chemical elements, we processing CO2 to O2, and try change Venus atmosphere composition

questions.text: What is the situation on station?

dialogAnswers.text: Many of worker were killed by that creatures, there is only three of us left here, station now under the enemy control

questions.text: I need to use the station communication system, to find something on the surface

dialogAnswers.text: First of all we need to activate the platform propulsion system to turn station
To access to the engine room you need Green Card, i give it to you but first we need to destroy most of enemy
Bring me evidence that enemy was destroyed, bring me at least 10 evidence and i give to you a Green Card
Did you destroy he enemy in factory

questions.text: One moment, let me check my inventory....

dialogAnswers.text: Thank you for the support, i hope you will find what you are looking for....
Hello i`m a station Engineer Striker, what can i help

Venus, a century ago people believed Venus is Second Earth a Twin sister, and now we are here and what we see... No tropical forest, no oceans, only the hot rocky desert and toxic atmosphere it can kill you in just a second . day is lasted about 116 Earth days

questions.text: Why you living on the hovering platforms

dialogAnswers.text: We cant build a surface base here Because of the extremely pressure over 100 atmospheres, per centimeter, and temperature powered by Green house Effect up to 650 C, it just crashed our structures, we try to understand how t build something in this environment, i almost forget there is a acid rain, almost anytime at altitude 35-50 km.

questions.text: So how do you get resource from surface and living here

dialogAnswers.text: we found the solution an air hovering platform on the altitude of 60km above the surface, at this altitude the pressure is equal to Earth, but the wind is blows with speed of 100 m/s that`s why we used a engine on the platform to reduce wind speed and hovering on the one point above the surface, we have some drones and manipulators to reach and drill the surface, but not for a long time, only 10 -15 minutes then drone is almost broken, we need fix it almost every time, that`s why we have a numerous workers and a worker city

questions.text: did you know something about Surface Scanner?

dialogAnswers.text: No talk to  Communication Engineer Parker or  Captain Turner, anyway that's all who left of the workers...
